data.description:
LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION!  . . . Welcome to a mid-century masterpiece nestled on a huge corner half acre lot in the coveted Golf Cart District of Ocean Springs - a prime location that harmoniously blends tranquility with the convenience of urban living. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, 1583 heated/cooled square feet, this home is an enchanting retreat in an area where many desire to live! There's also a warm and inviting versatile, extra space that currently serves as a 4th bedroom. 

As you step through the front door, you'll be captivated by the timeless charm of this mid-century modern gem. The open floor plan, large windows, and striking architectural details evoke a sense of nostalgia while embracing modern comforts.  This precious home also provides a heated and cooled sunroom, where natural light pours in, creating an inviting space that can be enjoyed year-round. This is the perfect place to unwind, work, or entertain, with views of the lush backyard and the shimmering inground pool.  If you are a lover of plants; this is the spot for you!

Outdoor enthusiasts will revel in the large entertainers' deck surrounding the pool. This is an ideal setting for barbecues, pool parties, or simply basking in the Mississippi sun. Imagine creating unforgettable memories with family and friends right in your own backyard. This home's prime placement in the Golf Cart District of Ocean Springs means you're a stone's throw away from the vibrant downtown scene. Discover a host of local eateries, charming boutiques, and lively bars that showcase Ocean Springs' unique character. Experience live music, dine at delightful local restaurants, and explore the hidden treasures of this charming coastal town.
